No. 09-1210 (R46-015). Dennis Hollingsworth, et al. v. Kristin M. Perry, et al. 559 U.S. 1118, 130 S. Ct. 2432,

176 L. Ed. 2d 945,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3874. May 10, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to this Court’s Rule 46.1.

Same case below, 591 F.3d 1147.
